Signed-off-by: Peter Zijlstra (Intel) <peterz@infradead.org>
Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org
Link: https://lkml.kernel.org/r/20250103-x86-collapse-flush-fix-v1-1-3c521856cfa6@google.com
